##Sample Utterance

HelloIntent hello
QuestionIntent question

MyNameIsIntent {firstname}
MyNameIsIntent my name is {firstname}

WhatIsMyNameIntent ask me what my name is

SayHelloIntent say hello to {firstname}
SayHelloIntent say hi to {firstname}
SayHelloIntent greet {firstname}

SayAgeIntent tell {firstname} he is {age}
SayAgeIntent tell {firstname} she is {age}
SayAgeIntent tell {firstname} he is {age} years old
SayAgeIntent tell {firstname} she is {age} years old

AddIntent add {first} plus {second}

LikesIntent I {preference} like pizza

DayCountIntent how many days away is {thedate}
ReverseDayCountIntent what day is {delta} from now


